  <summary date="2019-11-19T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Energy Efficient Commercial Buildings Act of 2019

This bill reinstates and extends that tax deduction for energy efficient commercial buildings through 2024. It also increases the maximum allowable amount of such deduction.

The bill modifies American Society of Heating, Refrigerating and Air-Conditioning Engineer (ASHRAE) standards and other efficiency standards for commercial buildings.</summary>
